data.description: BEAUTIFUL 4 BEDROOM 3 FULL BATHROOM HOME IN SIMPSONVILLE WITHIN WALKING DISTANCE TO ADAMS MILL YMCA. NEAR HOLLY TREE COUNTRY CLUB. MINUTES FROM DOWNTOWN SIMPSONVILLE AND FIVE FORKS. WHEN YOU WALK IN THE FOYER AREA THE FORMAL DINING ROOM IS ON YOUR RIGHT, WHICH FEATURES A BEAUTIFUL TRAY CEILING AND PLENTY OF NATURAL LIGHT. THE GREAT ROOM AREA AND KITCHEN ARE OPEN TO EACH OTHER. THE GREAT ROOM HAS A GAS FIREPLACE AND VAULTED CEILINGS. THE KITCHEN HAS STUNNING DARK WOOD CABINETS AND GRANITE COUNTER TOPS. THERE IS A NICE SIZE PANTRY AS WELL. THE SPACIOUS MASTER SUITE HAS A TRAY CEILING AND 2 NICE SIZE CLOSETS. THE MASTER BATHROOM HAS A GARDEN TUB AND SEPARATE SHOWER AS WELL AS A DOUBLE SINK VANITY WITH GRANITE COUNTER TOP. THERE ARE 2 MORE BEDROOMS DOWNSTAIRS AND A FULL BATHROOM WITH A TUB/SHOWER COMBO. UPSTAIRS IS THE MASSIVE 4TH BEDROOM THAT IS 25X14. THERE IS A FULL BATHROOM UPSTAIRS AS WELL. THERE IS A TERMITE BOND IN PLACE. THIS HOME WAS BUILT IN 2017. CALL FOR YOUR SHOWING APPOINTMENTS TODAY.
